id: pm-i04b
title: Deduplicate runtime terminal-status checks across query commands
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: multiple commands locally normalize status with normalizeStatusInput and then check statusRegistry.terminal_statuses. Representative copies include list.ts:80 isTerminal, search.ts:202 isTerminal, context.ts:328 normalizeStatusForRegistry and context.ts:348 isTerminal, close.ts:40, and dedupe-audit.ts:146. Existing status-normalization items are closed, and open pm-v798 is item-type normalization rather than runtime status registry helper reuse."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[3]: code-quality,dedup,status
created_at: "2026-05-22T19:16:34.739Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-24T08:21:15.305Z"
author: codex-duplicate-audit
acceptance_criteria: Shared runtime status helpers normalize configured statuses and test terminal membership; list/search/context/close/dedupe-audit use those helpers; custom status registry behavior remains covered; focused status/list/search tests and pnpm build pass.
parent: pm-rnpb
resolution: Shared runtime status helpers now centralize registry-aware normalization and terminal-status checks.
expected_result: list/search/context/close/dedupe-audit use one tested status helper path without behavior changes.
actual_result: PR #58 merged shared helpers in src/core/item/status.ts with focused tests and green CI.
comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-22T19:16:34.739Z",codex-duplicate-audit,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm search 'terminal status statusRegistry terminal_statuses isTerminal normalizeStatusInput' found closed historical status items and no active exact dedup item."
  "2026-05-24T06:43:07.905Z",terminal-status-dedup,"DONE (terminal-status-dedup): Extracted two shared runtime status helpers into src/core/item/status.ts: normalizeStatusForRegistry(status, registry) = normalizeStatusInput(status, registry) ?? status, and isTerminalStatus(status, registry) = registry.terminal_statuses.has(normalizeStatusForRegistry(status, registry)). These preserve the exact prior semantics (registry-aware normalization with raw-value fallback). Replaced the duplicated local isTerminal/normalizeStatusForRegistry blocks in 5 command files: list.ts (removed local isTerminal, 3 call sites -> isTerminalStatus), search.ts (removed local isTerminal, 2 call sites; dropped now-unused normalizeStatusInput import), close.ts (removed local isTerminal, 2 call sites; dropped now-unused ItemStatus import), context.ts (removed local normalizeStatusForRegistry + isTerminal, now imported from status.ts; 1 isTerminal call site -> isTerminalStatus), dedupe-audit.ts (local isTerminal now delegates to isTerminalStatus when dedupeStatusRegistry is set, preserving the module-state default-set fallback for the unreachable null path). status.ts is already in vitest.config.ts include (100% gated) so NO new include line is required. Extended tests/unit/status-normalization.spec.ts with describe blocks for normalizeStatusForRegistry (known/alias/raw-fallback) and isTerminalStatus (built-in terminal closed+canceled, non-terminal open+in_progress, custom registry terminal+alias+non-terminal, raw-fallback for unknown/blank) using resolveRuntimeStatusRegistry over SETTINGS_DEFAULTS.schema and a custom schema. tsc --noEmit: exit 0. Focused tests: 6 spec files (status-normalization, list/search/context/close/dedupe-audit command specs) all pass = 96 tests. Coordinator: CHANGELOG ### Changed bullet -> 'Extract shared isTerminalStatus/normalizeStatusForRegistry helpers to src/core/item/status.ts; deduplicate runtime terminal-status checks across list/search/context/close/dedupe-audit commands (pm-i04b)'."
  "2026-05-24T07:00:12.520Z",claude-code-agent,"COORDINATOR VERIFIED 2026-05-24: combined full coverage gate green (1621 tests, 100%), static-quality-gate passed (clones gone), typecheck clean. Dogfooded list/search/context/close terminal-status flows in temp repo — all correct."
  "2026-05-24T07:02:46.381Z",claude-code-agent,Submitted in PR #58 (branch recover-unreadable-toon-items-and-dedup-core-helpers).
